"quote","settings":{"rev_title":"","display_review":true,"display_review_text":true,"star_rating":5,"quote":"<p>Add customer reviews and testimonials to showcase your store's happy customers.<\/p>","author":"Add author name","authorsub":"Author Designation","color_scheme":""}}},"block_order":["quote_jxWgth","quote_ihniPz","quote_Piwcgb","quote_JTtUkM","quote_F4xYFD"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"title":"Testimonial","heading_size":"h2","head_align":"left","heading_color_scheme":"","head_space":true,"description":"","description_style":"body","text_size":"small","author_img_position":"below","author_direction":"column","image_corners":"rounded","columns_desktop":4,"enable_desktop_slider":true,"arrow_position":"inline","column_alignment":"center","space_around":20,"quote_img":false,"quote_color":"#ffbb40","star_ratingclr":"#ffbb40","color_scheme":"","swipe_on_mobile":true,"padding_top":60,"padding_bottom":60}},"featured_blog_e6jFPX":{"type":"featured-blog","disabled":true,"settings":{"heading":"Blog posts","heading_size":"h2","head_align":"left","heading_color_scheme":"","head_space":true,"description":"","description_style":"body","view_all_label":"View all blog","show_view_all":true,"view_button_pos":"top","view_all_style":"link","arrow_position":"inline","blog":"news","flex_direction":"column","image_height":"adapt","post_limit":3,"columns_desktop":3,"enable_desktop_slider":false,"show_image":true,"date_position":"below","show_date":true,"show_author":true,"show_comment":false,"show_tag":true,"show_seprator":true,"secerpt":"truncate","show_read_more_button":true,"read_more_uppercase":true,"read_more_style":"link","blog_card_style":"card","color_scheme":"","swipe_on_mobile":true,"padding_top":60,"padding_bottom":60}},"collapsible_content_MER3U4":{"type":"collapsible-content","blocks":{"collapsible_row_T8rhaY":{"type":"collapsible_row","settings":{"default_open":false,"heading":"What is the difference between fashion jewelry and fine jewelry?","icon":"question_mark","row_content":"<p>Fashion jewelry is typically made from more affordable materials like plated metals, cubic zirconia, and glass. It prioritizes trendy designs and caters to a wider range of budgets. Fine jewelry, on the other hand, uses precious metals like gold and platinum, often paired with gemstones like diamonds and sapphires. It is built for longevity and value.<\/p><p><\/p><p><br\/><\/p>","page":""}},"collapsible_row_izcPeR":{"type":"collapsible_row","settings":{"default_open":false,"heading":"What materials do you use in your jewelry?","icon":"question_mark","row_content":"<p>We use high-quality materials like kundan, cubic zirconia, pearls.  For detailed information on specific pieces, you can visit the product description page.<\/p>","page":""}},"collapsible_row_txBVJC":{"type":"collapsible_row","settings":{"default_open":false,"heading":"What kind of stones do we use in our jewellery?","icon":"question_mark","row_content":"<p>It varies from product to product. Most gemstone products have natural semi-precious stones, but you can go through the description of the product to verify the quality of the stones used in that specific product. We also use synthetic gemstones in various colours.<\/p><p>Wherever a synthetic stone is used, it is clearly mentioned in the product description. Please read the product description for all details. I q on the product, you may contact our customer service team.<\/p>","page":""}},"collapsible_row_6GXkPB":{"type":"collapsible_row","settings":{"default_open":false,"heading":"Is your jewelry hypoallergenic?","icon":"question_mark","row_content":"<p>We strive to use hypoallergenic materials whenever possible. However, sensitivities can vary. If you have specific allergies,  we recommend checking the product description for material details or contacting us for more information.<\/p>","page":""}},"collapsible_row_UV6f8P":{"type":"collapsible_row","settings":{"default_open":false,"heading":"Do you offer wholesale options?","icon":"question_mark","row_content":"<p>Please contact us for information on wholesale inquiries.<\/p>","page":""}}},"block_order":["collapsible_row_T8rhaY","collapsible_row_izcPeR","collapsible_row_txBVJC","collapsible_row_6GXkPB","collapsible_row_UV6f8P"],"settings":{"heading":"Frequently asked questions","heading_size":"h2","head_align":"left","heading_color_scheme":"background-1","head_space":true,"description":"","description_style":"body","layout":"section","color_scheme":"scheme-abe3bc68-5409-41dd-abcf-8f9ac474947a","secondary_background":false,"image_ratio":"adapt","desktop_layout":"image_second","padding_top":60,"padding_bottom":0}}},"order":["rich_text_B7E8LA","f4fc861e-a8e9-4733-8984-e73213d48588","scrolling_bar_UQtexc","7ff50e69-760a-4d45-ae67-4ede3191d751","image_with_text_GQY9ke","featured_collection_B9Xn9U","featured_collection_jXyVBy","featured_collection_URz8Ye","featured_collection_KxKRPA","collection_list_8Egf6z","collection_list_RRAGph","collection_list_znmXPV","multirow_ChLj6f","sponsored_product_4iwxQz","collection_list_3GgcAX","sponsored_product_TgFtkV","sponsored_product_qymxNC","17161831018646161b","collage_FXfDCd","testimonial_8JDWjV","featured_blog_e6jFPX","collapsible_content_MER3U4"]}